lead_paragraph: Kawhi Leonard scored 27 points and LaMarcus Aldridge added 26 to lead the San Antonio Spurs to 104-94 win over the Houston Rockets on Saturday night, tying the mark as the seventh-fastest team in NBA history to reach 50 wins.

headline.print_headline: Leonard Leads Spurs to 50th Win, 104-94 Over Rockets
